org.archive.wayback.replay.mimetype

Class SimpleMimeTypeDetector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.archive.wayback.replay.mimetype.SimpleMimeTypeDetector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MimeTypeDetector

    public class SimpleMimeTypeDetector
extends Object
implements MimeTypeDetector
    Simple MimeTypeDetector implementation. It's ad-hoc and not customizable, just tested against many samples.
